      <acqinfo id="aspace_a9758c7d7050eda836613a36eef03fb3">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Doolittle Collection of Japanese Drama was housed in the former Drama Library until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
